CFOxLxsUUkAoEyjRHh4nBA">Thương xuân - 傷春</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/Th%C3%A1i-Thu%E1%BA%ADn/author-l-NINz3JTJVTCX2aN0HlSQ">Thái Thuận</a>)<br>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/%C4%90o%C3%A0n-Huy%C3%AAn/Ti%E1%BB%85n-H%C6%B0ng-Nh%C3%A2n-L%C3%AA-do%C3%A3n-ph%C3%B3-khuy%E1%BA%BFt-k%E1%BB%B3-2/poem-vJRnpjaK_uLUJfrLRiPRYA">Tiễn Hưng Nhân Lê doãn phó khuyết kỳ 2 - 餞興仁犁尹赴闕其二</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/%C4%90o%C3%A0n-Huy%C3%AAn/author-h3EvqeQvlQUxq2sceUWWYQ">Đoàn Huyên</a>)<br>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/%C4%90%E1%BB%97-Ph%E1%BB%A7/T%E1%BB%91ng-%C4%90o%C3%A0n-c%C3%B4ng-t%C3%A0o-quy-Qu%E1%BA%A3ng-Ch%C3%A2u/poem-SNZuF-D8KCyutrxOiOglcg">Tống Đoàn công tào quy Quảng Châu - 送段功曹歸廣州</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/%C4%90%E1%BB%97-Ph%E1%BB%A7/author-Se3x2jWTezvoDpkpSU9qjg">Đỗ Phủ</a>)<br>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/Ti%C3%AAu-C%E1%BA%A5u/Xu%C3%A2n-thi/poem-7E6wITnxCld9Svvhs4uUkw">Xuân thi - 春詩</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/Ti%C3%AAu-C%E1%BA%A5u/author-Ae4EcQjuDrs0y-frjFfqIA">Tiêu Cấu</a>)<br></div>	</div>
